OL,3,CPolice officers under gross misconduct
OL,4,Cinvestigation in wrongful conviction
OL,5,Ccase
OL,7,FAndrew Malkinson, 58, spent 17 years
OL,8,Fin jail for a rape he did not commit
OL,9,Fafter he was convicted in 2004 for the
OL,10,Fattack on a woman in Little Hulton, in
OL,11,FSalford.
OL,13,FDespite the fact that he did not fit
OL,14,Fthe description given by witnesses, he
OL,15,Fwas handed a life sentence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
