OL,7,FIt said at the end of the
OL,8,Finvestigation, it will determine
OL,9,Fwhether there is an indication that
OL,10,Fanyone serving with the police may
OL,11,Fhave breached the standards of
OL,12,Fprofessional behaviour or if the case
OL,13,Fshould be referred to the Crown
OL,14,FProsecution Service.
OL,16,FMr Malkinson, from Grimsby, had his
OL,17,Fconviction quashed by the Court of
OL,18,FAppeal in July 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
