OL,7,FHe twice applied for his case to be
OL,8,Freferred for appeal by the Criminal
OL,9,FCases Review Commission (CCRC), but
OL,10,Fwas turned down.
OL,12,FMr Malkinson was eventually released
OL,13,Ffrom prison in December 2020.
OL,15,FThousands of convictions are now being
OL,16,Freviewed in the wake of his case.
OL,18,FThe CCRC has been told to look back
OL,19,Fover all cases which have the
OL,20,F"possibility of DNA opportunities".
