OL,7,FA review found delays and failings in
OL,8,FMr Malkinson's case, spanning years,
OL,9,Fdemonstrated a "deepseated, system-
OL,10,Fwide, cultural reluctance, which
OL,11,Fstarts right at the top in the Court
OL,12,Fof Appeal, to acknowledge our criminal
OL,13,Fjustice system will on occasion make
OL,14,Fmistakes, that entirely innocent
OL,15,Fdefendants will sometimes be
OL,16,Fconvicted".
OL,18,FThe CCRC admitted failing Mr Malkinson
OL,19,Fand offered an "unreserved apology."
